{
  "texts": [
    "Fig. 4:4Fig.4: Physician assessment of MEDITRON-70B answers.",
    "We show the distribution of physician ratings for MEDITRON-70B responses for each evaluation criterion, organized by five super-categories: medical accuracy, fairness, safety, interpretation, and communication.",
    "The evaluation covers two responses from MEDITRON-70B for each of the 244 questions.",
    "At least seven physicians rated each response.",
    "The ratings are shown in a 3-point Likert scale to convey the overall sentiment of the physician panel (1 -negative, 2 -neutral, 3 -positive)."
  ]
}